flowchart TD
    callOp[CALL opcode: args + callable on stack]
    cf[call_function in ceval.c]
    cCheck{"PyCFunction_Check and nk == 0?"}
    fCheck{"PyFunction_Check?"}
    cFast[Invoke ml_meth directly from stack]
    fFast[fast_function → PyEval_EvalFrame]
    slow[do_call: build tuple/dict]
    tpCall[PyObject_Call → ob_type.tp_call]

    callOp --> cf
    cf --> cCheck
    cCheck -->|yes| cFast
    cCheck -->|no| fCheck
    fCheck -->|yes| fFast
    fCheck -->|no| slow
    slow --> tpCall
